# --- secrets: never commit (relevant once dotfiles/desktop layers land) ---
# private keys & key material
*.key
*.pem
id_*
!id_*.pub
*_ed25519
!*_ed25519.pub
*_rsa
!*_rsa.pub
# ssh / gnupg / pki dirs if ever vendored in
**/.ssh/**
!**/.ssh/*.pub
!**/.ssh/config
**/.gnupg/**
**/.pki/**
# tool credentials / tokens / oauth
**/.credentials.json
**/oauth_creds.json
**/*credentials*
**/*token*
.netrc
.npmrc
# AI tool state that is not config
**/.claude.json
**/history.jsonl
**/*.history
**/shell-snapshots/**
**/sessions/**

# --- live disk artifacts from local verification ---
*.img
*.img.*

# --- editor / OS noise ---
*.swp
*~
.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc
